Process:

# source init1
Sets up local ssh agent on the Windows machine

# ./init2
Pulls an ssh certificate that gets the user into Planetlab

# ./startP2
Creates a port forwarder from a PlanetLab machine and starts the visualization

At this point, p2setup can be called on the controlling machine to start dissemination and startup of P2

# ./shutdown1
Kills the local ssh-agent

